title: [At Face Value]
description: Vibrant patchwork curtains adorn the single window, the sill lined with little miniatures of different towns that glisten in the moonlight.  A ramshackle case is pushed along one side, the wares within neatly arranged despite the chaos of the room.  A small table sits in the center of the room, topped with mirrors of different sizes and shapes.  A well-used travel trunk sits on the floor near a a purple patchwork partition.
